Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:03.67,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,見上げた夜空の星たちの光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.01,0:00:11.35,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,見上げた夜空の星たちの光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:34.68,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,一つ　二つ　鐘の音は響く心の中へと広く深く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:36.49,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,物語のような星の雫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:38.49,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,その中に细い线路を筑く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:42.34,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,时间とともに时代は动く 流れる星は静かに动く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:45.90,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,目を闭じて耳をすませば GOOD BYE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.73,0:00:49.39,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,放て光負けずに しっかり今
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.39,0:00:50.39,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,時を超え　誰かに届くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:54.12,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,栄光の光はこの向こうにキミたちとつくっていくストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.43,0:00:59.62,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,見上げた夜空の星達の光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:03.84,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,古の思い願いが時代超えいろあせるコトなく届く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:07.40,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,キラリ瞳に映る誰かの叫び
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:09.19,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,風に想いを　月に願いを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:11.59,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,力ある限り生きてくんだ　今日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:15.10,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,見上げた夜空の星達の光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:19.32,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,古の思い願いが時代超えいろあせるコトなく届く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.69,0:01:23.39,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕らの想いもいつか誰かの胸に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:26.91,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,光り続けよう　あの星のように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:03.67,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,举头仰望夜空繁星闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.01,0:00:11.35,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,举头仰望夜空繁星闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:34.68,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,一下 两下 钟声的余韵在心中回荡延展
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:36.49,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,像故事般的星之滴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:38.49,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,在其中构建出纤细的路线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:42.34,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,时代变迁 斗转星移
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:45.90,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,闭上双眼用心倾听 G O O D bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.73,0:00:49.39,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不输给光芒 坚决的穿越时代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.39,0:00:50.39,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,传递到某人的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:54.12,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,在荣耀之光的彼岸与你们一同创造故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.43,0:00:59.62,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,举头仰望夜空繁星闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:03.84,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,古老的思念穿越时代传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:07.40,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,闪动的眼瞳中映现出谁的呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:09.19,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,寄思念于风 诉心愿于明月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:11.59,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要拼尽全力的生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:15.10,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,举头仰望夜空繁星闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:19.32,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,古老的思念穿越时代传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.69,0:01:23.39,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的思念总有一天会达到某人的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:26.91,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,继续闪耀吧 就像那颗星星一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:38.04,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows who I really am
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:43.02,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,I never felt this empty before
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:47.63,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I ever need someone to come along
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:52.59,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna comfort me, and keep me strong
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:22:02.01,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,旅はまた続いてく  穏やかな日も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.56,0:22:12.30,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,月はまた新しい周期で 船を照らし出す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:21.61,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,祈りをささげて  新しい日を待つ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.33,0:22:31.10,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,鮮やかに  光る海  その果てまで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:33.29,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,へ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:38.04,ED_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人知道我究竟是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:43.02,ED_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前从未感觉到如此虚无空荡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:47.63,ED_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我需要有人来陪伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:52.59,ED_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,谁会安慰我并让我更加坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:22:02.01,ED_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,旅程还在继续 安稳的日子也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.56,0:22:12.30,ED_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,又一轮阴晴圆缺的月亮 映出了船的形状
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:21.61,ED_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,用心祈祷着 等候着新的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.33,0:22:31.10,ED_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,直到那色泽鲜艳的光之海 得偿所愿为止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:33.29,ED_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改造魂魄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.63,0:01:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为对抗虚而开发的虚拟魂魄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在计划成形之前遭到废除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该对所有的改造魂魄发出了破坏令
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.33,0:01:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样应该差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.48,0:01:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜助先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的错 出了这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不在意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么小雨要怕成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是伙伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会全部搞定的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜助先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 好了 乖乖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长 准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就去回收商品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙一人在那干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行动很容易看穿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 一护
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来指令了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桥上同学 金田同学 伊野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了 这么大声嚷嚷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个不认识的高中生来袭击我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘色头发的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你们是玩游戏玩入迷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那死神和那帮小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的好心情都被他们给搅合了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚 有虚的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我刚去过的那一带
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帮小鬼会被袭击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它消除吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 我再做个更好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 罚我们留堂打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不相信我们说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是因为我们平常品行不端
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 连游戏机也被没收了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电灵神器好象有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没电了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是那么喜欢恰比
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就应该多买点电池吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握不到虚的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:04:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚 刚才的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 一护
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:05:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来打扰我吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还只会东躲西藏的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不管你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没两下子就别强出头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所言极是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙怎么受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这是谁的身体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对付这种杂鱼你要都弄得遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不要战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是因为你迟迟不来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才战斗的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你这样也算是战斗用魂魄吗 真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要瞎来好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚的头被砍中 不用管它也会自动消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还特意又踢一脚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你们在逗老师玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没骗您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的 相信我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那满身是血的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是确实是有 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也拜托你们留堂打扫了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能这样 等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是很讨厌他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么做不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不救的话他们会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会杀任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被制作出来后 尸魂界马上就
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出台改造魂魄的废除令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚被制作完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来日就面临死期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都在药丸中颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着周遭的同伴日复一日的减少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同其他药丸混在一起幸运地逃出仓库后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一直在担心会不会被人发现废除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我颤抖不已时 我一直在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我的性命要由他人来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么自己没有决定权呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生也好死也罢都属于别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 所以我不会杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想看到人死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易让我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么遍体鳞伤呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下准备好的道具都派不上用场了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊 我还以为能大显身手一番呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:09:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么处置它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么处置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是废除啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得到我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是何方神圣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你问我是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个黑心商
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能把他拿走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 浦原
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你卖给客人的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不退钱就想抢回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也没辙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会退你钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很满意这商品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来你们就是在灵法范围外活动的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你们也没有义务将其回收吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是出了事 我们可不会出面的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.11,0:10:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无需担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最近已经习惯麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 一护
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道是别人的身体还胡来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听见了没 混球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁人看来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是相当奇怪的场景呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然还是不能释怀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亚 要怎么做才能直接向这家伙抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那肯定是把他注入灵魂出窍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是已死的肉体中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 尸体是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注入 注入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事没可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说只要有容器就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.05,0:11:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这也太扯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我现在的身体也不是活人的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0450,,{\fs25}【施工中给大家添麻烦了暂时请大家多多协助】
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是放到嘴里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.58,0:12:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我再一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好矮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.59,0:12:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊这是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会在布偶里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得好软
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 改造魂魄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你的话还没说完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就好好的慢慢的说个清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今我就用这副身体跟你决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床了 一护
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上了 morning morning
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我起来向我好好赔礼道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然的话 我就偷偷躲进你的书包里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你把我带到学校去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让班里的女生说你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎一护同学居然带着人偶 好恶心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就叽叽喳喳的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你老实的当个布偶嘛 魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂 是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改造魂魄叫着太拗口了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也就配叫魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不能叫魂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好没气魄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 用最前面改造的改怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我改吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改给人感觉很帅气 让我火大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大清早的吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不能安静的换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好角度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做布偶真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棉花都踩出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我开门了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岛同学和浅野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是一大早干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还大清早呢 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岛同学他们来找你一起上学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面包烤好了 吃完再走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 睡过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就下去 稍等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 真少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上人的记忆你又消掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的事情如果他们还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不好办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间发生太多事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且仿佛是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护 我先走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙贵 你也是选修美术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课题你做了吗 《未来的我》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了啊 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有自信的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将来要成为无差别格斗女冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我画得太差 拿不出手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织姬你呢 画了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于问我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.91,0:16:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这可是我非常引以为傲的作品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高时速380公里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴可以喷出2万度高温的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛可发射破坏光线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞错了啊 织姬 你画得不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想留堂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 还没讲完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 黑崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 早上好啊 井上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎同学今天好像心情不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是吧 织姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小满 今天几号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6月16号 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是心情好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙露出那种表情的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他心情最差的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙贵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道原因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天不会来学校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0450,,{\fs25}【深感抱歉明天17日将休诊一天 黑崎医院】
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在开始召开会议决定明天的任务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽这么说 掌事的还是老爸我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有决定权也在老爸我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 这样不叫会议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要发言请先举手 参谋长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参谋长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【并非完全不同意】
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游子还是一如既往担任便当参谋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏梨负责拿行李
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那长官你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你老爸我剪头发了 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 你看仔细呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的家庭会议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吗 明天逃课去野炊什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野炊 不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天休息一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从早上开始就怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是忌日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是我妈的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不能这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确来说不是忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是被杀的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 早上好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙明天不会来学校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 如果我是雨的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否像永远无法交汇的天空同大地连接起来一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接到某人的心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 上啊上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 再来一次 这次一定不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 我有点事要去办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 今天有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十三番队 朽木露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:20:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大小姐怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在人间界的停留时间超过了限制
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 不是因为这点事才叫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定另有内情 你去调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.09,0:21:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微粗暴点也无妨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位朽木露琪亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.82,0:22:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人震惊的推理片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.22,0:22:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎一心连续杀人事件
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.64,0:22:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美女护士封印在安德鲁之地的疯狂饺子盛宴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.12,0:22:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和悲壮的父亲的汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有那种节目
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有简单菜肴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
